{"tid":628046,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中區電梯上偷拍女子裙底　色狼遇休班警斷正","createTime":"2018-04-13T12:56:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T13:13:51.000Z","uid":5195,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"09bc33b0a540d1a99c161f88d10826ffafa0b5c2","tid":628046,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:56:53.000Z","msg":"一名駐守中區警署的警員，下午1時許，休班行經中區干諾道中一條扶手電梯時，發現前方有一名男子鬼鬼祟祟，持手機有所動作，而對上正有一名穿裙女子乘電梯，休班警驚覺他在偷拍女子裙底，於是上前截停查問，對方反抗，有途人見狀，助休班警合力將色狼制服並報警，其他警員到場調查後，以涉嫌破壞公眾體統將姓陳（44歲）男子拘捕。案中女事主25歲，事後協助警方調查，案件交由中區警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180413/photo/bkn-20180413190109376-0413_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180413194247\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180413%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180413190109376-0413_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180413194247&h=837b12b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n涉嫌偷拍女子裙底的男子被押上警車。(警方圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180413/bkn-20180413190109376-0413_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180413%2Fbkn-20180413190109376-0413_00822_001.html&d=NLRT3BKytKoMD2lY%2F%2BqSXk4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=468e0b51\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180413/bkn-20180413190109376-0413_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8c742b734ce68b519de6954824e0f1c3ff1e5178","tid":628046,"uid":175523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8efc2882796f9a6055445ab4affcacae0cd7d05","tid":628046,"uid":11809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:58:57.000Z","msg":"N3午餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"791da53d7964dcf67634cdecaa33043eb093f6d6","tid":628046,